    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Horror Adventures pg. 145</em></p><p><strong>Type</strong> regional curse; <strong>Save</strong> Will DC 19</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> As per major perilous demesne, except up to six hazards, each of CR 10 or less, imperil creatures in the area. The hazards are arranged so that if any are encountered together, the encounter's effective CR from hazards must be no more than 11 (for instance, two CR 9 hazards could be encountered together).</p><p><strong>Cure</strong> <em>Remove curse</em> removes a greater perilous demesne only if followed by a casting of <em>hallow</em> at the effect's center.</p>",
